#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.37:0.2"
msgid "4. Sīsapāvanavagga "
msgstr "4. In a Rosewood Forest "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 37. Paṭhamasūriyasutta → suriyūpamasuttaṃ (bj) | suriyupamā 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.37:0.3"
msgid "37. Paṭhamasūriyasutta "
msgstr "37. The Simile of the Sun (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: Sūriyassa → suriyassa (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.37:1.1"
msgid "“Sūriyassa, bhikkhave, udayato etaṃ pubbaṅgamaṃ etaṃ pubbanimittaṃ, yadidaṃ—aruṇuggaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, the dawn is the forerunner and precursor of the sunrise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.37:1.2"
msgid "Evameva kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ yathābhūtaṃ abhisamayāya etaṃ pubbaṅgamaṃ etaṃ pubbanimittaṃ, yadidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi. "
msgstr "In the same way, right view is the forerunner and precursor of truly comprehending the four noble truths. "

# NOTE: See BB on variant
msgctxt "sn56.37:1.3"
msgid "Tassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ: "
msgstr "A mendicant with right view can expect to truly understand: "

msgctxt "sn56.37:1.4"
msgid "‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānissati … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānissati. "
msgstr "‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.37:2.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.37:2.2"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

